              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "The difference is in the full system. Running ads without an optimized page wastes spend on traffic that leaves. Running SEO without a paid channel means missing buyers who are ready to call today. Dominion.Digital builds both together, connected to tracked landing pages, so every dollar spent is accountable and every lead is attributed to a source."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What kinds of businesses does local lead generation work for?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Local service businesses in Kansas City with a defined service area and a consistent average job value. Contractors, home services, professional services, medical and wellness, and similar businesses where a new customer has clear, measurable value. Dominion.Digital does a lead audit before starting to confirm the numbers make sense."
            }
