                  <p class="font-body text-text" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Monthly pipeline review</p>
                  <p class="font-body text-text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;"><strong style="font-weight: 800; color: #f0ebe1;">Dominion</strong><span style="color: #c8511a;">.</span><span style="font-weight: 400; color: #f0ebe1;">Digital</span> reviews results with you monthly, adjusts strategy based on what's producing, and sets priorities for the next period</p>
